Rating: 4
I loved this recipe. It will be a great addition to our rotation, especially in the spring and summer. I made it with all the ingredients it called for (you should buy the fresh spices!). Like others, I added a little extra lemon. Make sure the water you put in the bulgur is really hot, and double-check that ALL the bulgur is tender before mixing it in.

